Class BaseAssociations

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Associations

    public abstract class BaseAssociations
extends DefaultHashMap<java.lang.Integer,java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>>
    The Class BaseAssociations keeps all the associations and index the groups in the fragment in order to speed up the get of rows in groups. The indices are automatically created upon put and changed accordingly to other map operations. A set of full groups in every fragment in kept in order to speed up the check of full groups.
